/>\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/851753/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/851753/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">中國官方英文報章</span>《中國日報》:  簽證與否屬主權　其他政府不得干涉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/852717/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/852717/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指「支那化」是很惡毒標籤　《<span style=\"color: gold;\">環時</span>》促馬凱反思：少了他，不損港言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/851094/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/851094/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【FCC副主席續簽被拒】<span style=\"color: gold;\">中國外交部</span>：<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中央堅定支持</span></span>特區政府依法處理有關事務　任何外國無權干預<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/850521/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/850521/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外交部都分割獨立出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b79f1d1c1e433e31faea380edddb55f02ba8a68","tid":852881,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df2465da0ce714579aca7f1539a0e2dee3dd62bf","tid":852881,"uid":66686,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"quote":{"pid":"4d019a7bbbc978ded16888c4515d16de00efaa99","tid":852881,"uid":550,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:44:04.000Z","msg":"一早知係班奴才懶叻邀功啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好地地等佢丟淡少少先算帳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/08/154648_0ef1aba45f6b074921b2c3744a535a1d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F08%2F154648_0ef1aba45f6b074921b2c3744a535a1d.png&h=cd5e05da&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T08:03:24.000Z","msg":"肥彭幾時都講得岩"},{"pid":"53791630fa